  "title": "Facilities Technician 3 Months - 1 Year Contract @ Novena **Up to $3.5k OFFICE HOURS #HDTT",
  "description": "<p>3 Months extendable to 1 Year Contract - 1 Month bonus upon completion of 1 Year Contract</p><p><br /></p><p>Job Description:</p><ul><li>Perform plan preventive maintenance work (PPM) as assigned by the Supervisor.</li><li>Troubleshoot electrical fault and reinstate the power supply and equipment back to normal operation.</li><li>Troubleshoot air conditioning fault and reinstate the air conditioning back to normal operation.</li><li>Repair water pipe burst, mechanical work, medical gases system and other related facilities equipment.</li><li>Any other duties assigned by the Senior Technician/Engineer.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Min ITE Diploma</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>For interested candidate, please email your resumes to denyse.tan@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p><br /></p><p>Denyse Nicole Tan Shuqin (#HDT)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>CEI No: R1333503</p><p>Company EA license : 99C4599</p><p><br /></p>",
